Content:
Happy New Year All!
I pucked up an 81 GS450 that came with some extra forks. We thought they were from another GS, but they are air adjustable and measure 35mm vs the ones on the GS at 33mm. There is a Suzuki label on one. The dull aluminum things on the bottom appear to be hydraulic? There is a hole for a banjo bolt and a bleed screw. Never saw these before...
Title: Mystery Forks
Author: spduffee
